text: Matthew Temple (born 20 June 1999) is an Australian swimmer. He competed in the men's 200 metre butterfly at the 2019 World Aquatics Championships, placing 10th in his semi final. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1999 births Category:Australian male swimmers Category:Living people Category:Male butterfly swimmers Category:Male freestyle swimmers Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:World Aquatics Championships medalists in swimming
